nazariya:
CRUD — Create, Read, Update, Delete operatsiyalari. MongoDB da bu operatsiyalar SQL dan farqli sintaksisda, lekin bir xil maqsadda ishlatiladi.

## CREATE (Yaratish)

**insertOne()** — bitta document qo'shish:
```javascript
db.products.insertOne({
  name: 'Laptop',
  price: 1200,
  brand: 'Dell',
  inStock: true,
  tags: ['electronics', 'computer'],
  specs: { ram: '16GB', storage: '512GB' }
})
```

**insertMany()** — ko'p document qo'shish:
```javascript
db.products.insertMany([
  { name: 'Phone', price: 800, brand: 'Samsung' },
  { name: 'Tablet', price: 600, brand: 'Apple' },
  { name: 'Monitor', price: 400, brand: 'LG' }
])
```

## READ (O'qish)

**find()** — documentlarni topish:
```javascript
// Barcha documentlar
db.products.find()

// Filter bilan
db.products.find({ brand: 'Dell' })

// Projection (kerakli fieldlarni tanlash)
db.products.find({ brand: 'Dell' }, { name: 1, price: 1, _id: 0 })

// Birinchi mos kelgan document
db.products.findOne({ name: 'Laptop' })

// Saralash (1=o'sish, -1=kamayish)
db.products.find().sort({ price: -1 })

// Cheklash
db.products.find().limit(2)

// O'tkazib yuborish
db.products.find().skip(1).limit(2)

// Hisoblash
db.products.countDocuments({ brand: 'Dell' })
```

## UPDATE (Yangilash)

**updateOne()** — bitta document yangilash:
```javascript
// $set — fieldni yangilash
db.products.updateOne(
  { name: 'Laptop' },        // filter
  { $set: { price: 1100 } }  // yangilash
)

// $inc — raqamni oshirish/kamaytirish
db.products.updateOne(
  { name: 'Phone' },
  { $inc: { price: 50 } }  // price ga 50 qo'shish
)

// $push — arraygaga element qo'shish
db.products.updateOne(
  { name: 'Laptop' },
  { $push: { tags: 'sale' } }
)
```

**updateMany()** — ko'p document yangilash:
```javascript
db.products.updateMany(
  { brand: 'Dell' },
  { $set: { discount: true } }
)
```

**upsert** — topilmasa yaratish:
```javascript
db.products.updateOne(
  { name: 'Keyboard' },
  { $set: { price: 50, brand: 'Logitech' } },
  { upsert: true }  // topilmasa yangi document yaratadi
)
```

## DELETE (O'chirish)

```javascript
// Bitta document o'chirish
db.products.deleteOne({ name: 'Monitor' })

// Ko'p document o'chirish
db.products.deleteMany({ brand: 'LG' })

// Barcha documentlarni o'chirish
db.products.deleteMany({})
```

## Replace vs Update
```javascript
// replaceOne — butun documentni almashtirish
db.products.replaceOne(
  { name: 'Tablet' },
  { name: 'Tablet', price: 700, brand: 'Apple', newField: true }
)
// Diqqat: replaceOne da eski fieldlar yo'qoladi!
// updateOne $set da esa faqat ko'rsatilgan fieldlar o'zgaradi
```

