nazariya:
MongoDB da ma'lumotlarni filterlash uchun maxsus query operatorlar ishlatiladi. Bu operatorlar SQL dagi WHERE shartlariga o'xshaydi.

## Taqqoslash operatorlari (Comparison Operators)

```javascript
// $eq — teng (equal)
db.users.find({ age: { $eq: 25 } })
// Soddaroq yozuv:
db.users.find({ age: 25 })

// $ne — teng emas (not equal)
db.users.find({ status: { $ne: 'inactive' } })

// $gt — katta (greater than)
db.users.find({ xp: { $gt: 100 } })

// $gte — katta yoki teng (greater than or equal)
db.users.find({ age: { $gte: 18 } })

// $lt — kichik (less than)
db.users.find({ price: { $lt: 500 } })

// $lte — kichik yoki teng (less than or equal)
db.users.find({ rating: { $lte: 3 } })

// $in — ro'yxatdagi qiymatlardan biri
db.users.find({ course: { $in: ['Python', 'Web', 'Data Analysis'] } })

// $nin — ro'yxatdagi qiymatlardan hech biri emas
db.users.find({ city: { $nin: ['Toshkent', 'Samarkand'] } })
```

## Mantiqiy operatorlar (Logical Operators)

```javascript
// $and — barcha shartlar bajarilishi kerak
db.products.find({
  $and: [
    { price: { $gte: 100 } },
    { price: { $lte: 500 } },
    { inStock: true }
  ]
})

// Soddaroq AND (bir field bo'lsa):
db.products.find({ price: { $gte: 100, $lte: 500 } })

// $or — shartlardan biri bajarilsa kifoya
db.users.find({
  $or: [
    { course: 'Python' },
    { xp: { $gt: 300 } }
  ]
})

// $nor — hech biri bajarilmasligi kerak
db.users.find({
  $nor: [
    { status: 'banned' },
    { xp: { $lt: 0 } }
  ]
})

// $not — shartni inkor qilish
db.users.find({ age: { $not: { $gt: 60 } } })
```

## Element operatorlari

```javascript
// $exists — field mavjudligini tekshirish
db.users.find({ phone: { $exists: true } })
db.users.find({ email: { $exists: false } })

// $type — field tipini tekshirish
db.users.find({ age: { $type: 'number' } })
db.users.find({ name: { $type: 'string' } })
```

## Array operatorlari

```javascript
// $all — arrayda barcha qiymatlar bo'lishi
db.products.find({ tags: { $all: ['electronics', 'sale'] } })

// $size — array uzunligi
db.products.find({ tags: { $size: 3 } })

// $elemMatch — array elementi shartga mos kelishi
db.orders.find({
  items: { $elemMatch: { price: { $gt: 100 }, qty: { $gte: 2 } } }
})
```

## Regex operatori

```javascript
// $regex — pattern bo'yicha qidirish
db.users.find({ name: { $regex: /^Ali/i } })  // Ali bilan boshlanuvchilar
db.products.find({ description: { $regex: 'laptop', $options: 'i' } })
```

## Amaliy misol — murakkab query

```javascript
// SYNAPSE platformasida: Python yoki Web kursidagi,
// XP 100 dan katta, va hali premium emas foydalanuvchilar
db.users.find({
  $and: [
    { course: { $in: ['Python', 'Web'] } },
    { xp: { $gt: 100 } },
    { isPremium: { $ne: true } }
  ]
}).sort({ xp: -1 }).limit(10)
```

