nazariya:
Aggregation Pipeline — bu MongoDB da ma'lumotlarni qayta ishlash va tahlil qilish uchun ishlatiladigan kuchli mexanizm. U SQL dagi GROUP BY, JOIN, HAVING, SUM kabi funksiyalarni o'z ichiga oladi.

Pipeline — bu bosqichlar (stage) ketma-ketligi. Har bir bosqich oldingi bosqich natijasini qabul qilib, o'zgartiradi va keyingiga uzatadi.

```javascript
db.collection.aggregate([
  { $stage1: { ... } },
  { $stage2: { ... } },
  { $stage3: { ... } }
])
```

## Asosiy Pipeline Stage'lar

### $match — filterlash (SQL: WHERE)
```javascript
{ $match: { course: 'Python', xp: { $gt: 100 } } }
```

### $group — guruhlash (SQL: GROUP BY)
```javascript
{ $group: {
  _id: '$course',           // guruhlash kaliti
  totalUsers: { $sum: 1 },  // har guruhda nechta user
  avgXP: { $avg: '$xp' },   // o'rtacha XP
  maxXP: { $max: '$xp' },   // maksimal XP
  minXP: { $min: '$xp' },   // minimal XP
  totalXP: { $sum: '$xp' }  // umumiy XP
}}
```

### $project — fieldlarni tanlash/o'zgartirish (SQL: SELECT)
```javascript
{ $project: {
  name: 1,
  course: 1,
  _id: 0,
  // Hisoblash
  level: { $floor: { $divide: ['$xp', 100] } }
}}
```

### $sort — saralash (SQL: ORDER BY)
```javascript
{ $sort: { totalUsers: -1 } }
```

### $limit va $skip — sahifalash
```javascript
{ $limit: 5 }
{ $skip: 10 }
```

### $unwind — arrayni yoyish
```javascript
// tags: ['python', 'web'] bo'lsa, har tag uchun alohida document yaratadi
{ $unwind: '$tags' }
```

### $lookup — join qilish (SQL: JOIN)
```javascript
{ $lookup: {
  from: 'orders',           // boshqa collection
  localField: 'userId',    // joriy collection field
  foreignField: '_id',     // boshqa collection field
  as: 'userOrders'         // natija field nomi
}}
```

### $addFields — yangi field qo'shish
```javascript
{ $addFields: {
  fullName: { $concat: ['$firstName', ' ', '$lastName'] },
  isTopLearner: { $gt: ['$xp', 500] }
}}
```

## Amaliy misol — Kurs bo'yicha statistika

```javascript
db.users.aggregate([
  // 1. Faqat aktiv userlar
  { $match: { status: 'active' } },

  // 2. Kurs bo'yicha guruhlash
  { $group: {
    _id: '$course',
    userCount: { $sum: 1 },
    avgXP: { $avg: '$xp' },
    topXP: { $max: '$xp' }
  }},

  // 3. User soni bo'yicha kamayish tartibida
  { $sort: { userCount: -1 } },

  // 4. Faqat kerakli fieldlar
  { $project: {
    course: '$_id',
    userCount: 1,
    avgXP: { $round: ['$avgXP', 1] },
    topXP: 1,
    _id: 0
  }}
])
```

## $facet — parallel pipelinelar
```javascript
db.products.aggregate([
  { $facet: {
    byCategory: [
      { $group: { _id: '$category', count: { $sum: 1 } } }
    ],
    priceStats: [
      { $group: { _id: null, avgPrice: { $avg: '$price' }, maxPrice: { $max: '$price' } } }
    ]
  }}
])
```

Aggregation pipeline MongoDB ning eng kuchli xususiyatlaridan biri bo'lib, real-time analytics, reporting va data transformation uchun keng qo'llaniladi.

