nazariya:
Index — bu ma'lumotlar bazasida tezkor qidiruv uchun ishlatiladigan maxsus ma'lumot strukturasi. Indexsiz MongoDB har bir document ni ko'rib chiqadi (collection scan), indeks bilan esa faqat mos documentlarga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri murojaat qiladi.

## Index turlari

### 1. Single Field Index
```javascript
// email field bo'yicha index yaratish
db.users.createIndex({ email: 1 })  // 1=o'sish, -1=kamayish

// Unique index (takrorlanmasin)
db.users.createIndex({ email: 1 }, { unique: true })

// Index o'chirish
db.users.dropIndex({ email: 1 })

// Barcha indexlarni ko'rish
db.users.getIndexes()
```

### 2. Compound Index (ko'p field)
```javascript
// Birinchi course bo'yicha, keyin xp bo'yicha sort qilinsa
db.users.createIndex({ course: 1, xp: -1 })

// Compound index ishlatiladi:
db.users.find({ course: 'Python' }).sort({ xp: -1 })  // ✓
db.users.find({ course: 'Python' })                   // ✓ (prefix)
// Ishlatilmaydi:
db.users.find().sort({ xp: -1 })                      // ✗ (prefix yo'q)
```

### 3. Text Index (matn qidiruvi)
```javascript
db.articles.createIndex({ title: 'text', content: 'text' })

// Text search
db.articles.find({ $text: { $search: 'mongodb tutorial' } })

// Relevance score bo'yicha sort
db.articles.find(
  { $text: { $search: 'mongodb' } },
  { score: { $meta: 'textScore' } }
).sort({ score: { $meta: 'textScore' } })
```

### 4. Sparse Index
```javascript
// Faqat field mavjud bo'lgan documentlarga index
db.users.createIndex({ phone: 1 }, { sparse: true })
```

### 5. TTL Index (Time To Live)
```javascript
// 1 soatdan keyin avtomatik o'chirish
db.sessions.createIndex(
  { createdAt: 1 },
  { expireAfterSeconds: 3600 }
)
```

## explain() — Query tahlili

```javascript
// Query qanday ishlaganini ko'rish
db.users.find({ email: 'ali@gmail.com' }).explain('executionStats')

// Muhim ko'rsatkichlar:
// - stage: 'COLLSCAN' — index yo'q (sekin!)
// - stage: 'IXSCAN'  — index ishlatilmoqda (tez!)
// - docsExamined: nechta document ko'rilgan
// - executionTimeMillis: necha millisekund
```

## Optimallashtirish qoidalari

**1. ESR qoidasi (Equality, Sort, Range):**
```javascript
// Compound index tartibini to'g'ri qilish:
// Avval: Equality (=) fieldlari
// Keyin: Sort fieldlari
// Oxirda: Range ($gt, $lt) fieldlari
db.users.createIndex({ course: 1, xp: 1, age: 1 })

// Bu query uchun ideal:
db.users.find({ course: 'Python', age: { $gt: 18 } }).sort({ xp: 1 })
```

**2. Projection ishlatish:**
```javascript
// Faqat kerakli fieldlarni olish (tezroq)
db.users.find({ course: 'Python' }, { name: 1, xp: 1, _id: 0 })
```

**3. countDocuments vs count:**
```javascript
// To'g'ri va aniq
db.users.countDocuments({ course: 'Python' })
```

**4. Index yaratishda e'tibor berish:**
- Ko'p yoziladigan collectionda ko'p index = yozish sekinlashadi
- Kam ishlatilgan indexlar keraksiz joy oladi
- Compound index ko'p single indexni almashtira oladi

## Wildcard Index
```javascript
// Barcha fieldlar bo'yicha index
db.collection.createIndex({ '$**': 1 })
```

